Thursday, August 15, 2013

   An easy way to meet the whole grain requirements your body needs is to
   switch your pasta to whole grain. You can do this gradually by using
   half whole grain, and mix it with what you would normally use. Then
   make the switch completely to whole grain. It has a great flavor, and
   if you are trying to entice your kids to be healthier, this is an easy
   way to get it in their diets and even yours!
