About Me

   The NCCU Student Nutrition Association is a student led group focused
   on nutrition and wellness of the NCCU and surrounding community. The
   organization offers professional development to dietetics students and
   health-related education to the community.
   The SNA sponsors events, provides nutrition education to the community,
   and offers opportunities for professional development.

